GLPK 4.44 Attribution and Patch Files
======================================

This directory contains the GLPK (GNU Linear Programming Kit) version 4.44
attribution and patch files that were bundled with the original dwsolver source
distribution.

GLPK_AUTHORS   - GLPK authors
GLPK_INSTALL   - GLPK installation instructions
GLPK_NEWS      - GLPK changelog/news
GLPK_README    - GLPK readme
GLPK_THANKS    - GLPK acknowledgements
glpk-4.44.ThreadReady.patch - Thread-safety patch applied to the embedded GLPK sources

The embedded GLPK C sources live in src/ alongside the dwsolver source files.
GLPK is licensed under the GNU General Public License; see COPYING at the
repository root.
